    IntToStr(GetARGBJava(Fcustomcolor, colbrWhite)) + '@10' + '|' +
    //'@30|url@https://images.tokopedia.net/img/cache/200-square/VqbcmM/2020/10/18/e93d8df2-2671-41e8-9d75-087b8e23cf23.jpg.webp?ect=4g|Parts item '+inttostr(i+1)+
